#. 7: reset_colour
msgctxt "Revival00_1"
msgid ""
"Thanks to you,<1.pa> my power has been\n"
"returned to me.\n"
"\n"
"And I think you'll agreeâ€”a good deed\n"
"deserves a good reward.\n"
"\n"
"I can <2.se_co>enhance <3.re_co>your <4.se_co>clothing<5.re_co>, but I\n"
"require the necessary <6.se_co>materials<7.re_co> to do it."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Ah, you've come here again?<2.pa>\n"
"OK, let me see your clothes."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hrm... <2.pa>So long for now, I suppose?<3.pa>\n"
"Once you have some clothing you\n"
"want to upgrade, come back anytime."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "Talk02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hm...<2.pa> It seems like a few of my sisters\n"
"haven't yet recovered their power.\n"
"\n"
"Once they have their power back, I can\n"
"make your clothes even stronger."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Talk04"
msgid "One moment..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
msgctxt "Talk06"
msgid "<1.so>There we go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Talk08"
msgid "Then please choose some clothes for me."
msgstr ""

#. 1: choice
msgctxt "Talk09"
msgid ""
"Any other clothing items you want me to\n"
"work on?<1.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: pause (short)
msgctxt "Talk10"
msgid ""
"I can't enhance your clothing,<1.pa>\n"
"but let me tell you why..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Talk11"
msgid ""
"Oh! You don't have any clothes at all?\n"
"Well, if you get some, come back and\n"
"I'll see if I can enhance them for you."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
#. 5: choice
msgctxt "Talk12"
msgid ""
"<1.so>With the power available to me...<2.pa>\n"
"I should be able to enhance your\n"
"clothing <3.se_co>a little bit<4.re_co>.<5.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
#. 5: choice
msgctxt "Talk13"
msgid ""
"<1.so>With the power available to me...<2.pa>\n"
"I can enhance your clothing\n"
"<3.se_co>a fair amount<4.re_co>.<5.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
#. 5: choice
msgctxt "Talk14"
msgid ""
"<1.so>With the power available to me...<2.pa>\n"
"I can <3.se_co>greatly <4.re_co>enhance your clothing.<5.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: set_colour (red)
#. 4: reset_colour
#. 5: choice
msgctxt "Talk15"
msgid ""
"<1.so>With the power available to me...<2.pa>\n"
"I can enhance your clothing <3.se_co>to the max<4.re_co>.<5.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk16"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You've freed all of my sisters?<2.pa> I cannot\n"
"thank you enough...<3.pa> Anytime you need\n"
"our power, we'll be waiting."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "Talk17"
msgid "See you later."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk18"
msgid "<1.so>And... <2.pa>Here!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk19"
msgid "<1.so>Here I am, <2.pa>at your service!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
msgctxt "Talk20"
msgid "<1.so>Here I am!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
msgctxt "Talk21"
msgid "<1.so>Ready to help!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: variable (Shop_SelectItemName)
#. 3: choice
msgctxt "Talk22"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Now then, I'll enhance the\n"
"<2.va>.<3.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: variable (Shop_SelectItemName)
#. 4: pause (short)
#. 5: choice
msgctxt "Talk23"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hrm... <2.pa>You want the \n"
"<3.va><4.pa>\n"
"enhanced, correct?<5.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: variable (Shop_SelectItemName)
#. 3: choice
msgctxt "Talk24"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You're telling me to enhance the\n"
"<2.va>?<3.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: variable (Shop_SelectItemName)
#. 3: choice
msgctxt "Talk25"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You want to enhance the\n"
"<2.va>, correct? <3.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk26"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Sorry, <2.pa>there are some clothes,<3.pa> even with\n"
"my powers, that cannot be enhanced..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk27"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Sorry, but I can't enhance that clothing\n"
"item.<2.pa> Choose a different one."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk28"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Seems like that clothing item can't be\n"
"enhanced.<2.pa> Please choose something\n"
"else."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk29"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Seems like that clothing item can't be\n"
"enhanced.<2.pa> How about another piece\n"
"of clothing?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk30"
msgid ""
"<1.so>That clothing item can't be enhanced\n"
"with my power alone.<2.pa> But if my sisters\n"
"regained their powers..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "Talk31"
msgid ""
"<1.so>If you want me to enhance that clothing\n"
"item,<2.pa> I will need the help of my sisters..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk32"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Don't be unreasonable.<2.pa> Though, if my\n"
"sisters were awakened, it might be a\n"
"different story..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk33"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You... Please go help my sisters.<2.pa>\n"
"Doing so will allow me to enhance that\n"
"piece of clothing."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk34"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Even if I wanted to, you don't have \n"
"enough materials.<2.pa> Be on your way, and\n"
"think about bringing me what I need."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk35"
msgid ""
"<1.so>What absurdity!<2.pa> You don't have enough\n"
"materials to enhance that!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
msgctxt "Talk36"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Don't make excuses... You haven't got\n"
"enough materials."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk37"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You don't have enough materials.<2.pa>\n"
"How about another piece of clothing?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk38"
msgid "What? <1.pa>You want to stop?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: pause (short)
msgctxt "Talk39"
msgid ""
"Are you...<1.pa>are you going to make\n"
"ME wait?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: pause (short)
msgctxt "Talk40"
msgid "What is it? <1.pa>Hurry up and choose."
msgstr ""

#. 1: pause (short)
msgctxt "Talk41"
msgid "Hrm... <1.pa>You want to choose again?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk42"
msgid "Good<1.pa>-bye!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk43"
msgid "So <1.pa>long!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk44"
msgid "And <1.pa>gone!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk45"
msgid "See <1.pa>ya!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: choice
msgctxt "Talk46"
msgid ""
"<1.so>...However, you are lacking any clothing\n"
"that I can enhance.\n"
"\n"
"Here, <2.pa>let's take a look. Maybe I can\n"
"see what's stopping me from helping.<3.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: pause (short)
#. 2: pause (short)
msgctxt "Talk47"
msgid ""
"Hrm... <1.pa>I wanted to enhance other pieces\n"
"of clothing,<2.pa> but that does not seem\n"
"possible."
msgstr ""

#. 1: pause (short)
msgctxt "Talk48"
msgid ""
"If you get clothes and materials or if you\n"
"restore my sisters' powers,<1.pa> then I believe\n"
"I can help you."
msgstr ""

#. 1: pause (short)
msgctxt "Talk49"
msgid ""
"If you get new clothes and materials,<1.pa>\n"
"you should return to me."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound2
#. 2: pause (longer)
msgctxt "Talk50"
msgid ""
"<1.so>There we go.<2.pa>\n"
"Oh, while you're here...\n"
"\n"
"Some sets, if you enhance all parts of\n"
"them twice, can give you a nice extra\n"
"set bonus when you wear them.\n"
"This isn't true of everything I can\n"
"enhance, sadly..."
msgstr ""

